{"word":"ἔνδηλος","slug":"ἔνδηλος","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ἔνδηλος</b></el> <el>(ἔν-δηλος, ον) </el>adj (e)n-dhl os_on) <p/><br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b>= <a href='S:δῆλος'><el>δῆλος</el></a>,\n<p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>visible, manifest, clear</i>, <b><a href='S:Sophocles'>Soph.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Thucydides'>Thuc.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b>of persons, <i>manifest, discovered, known</i>, <b><a href='S:Aristophanes'>Ar.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Thucydides'>Thuc.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b><a href='S:Adverb'>adv.</a> <el>-λως</el>, <a href='S:Superlative'>Sup.</a> <el>-ότατα</el>, <b><a href='S:Thucydides'>Thuc.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}